  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Upgrade Your Coring Operation Today</h2>
      <p>Equip your team with the best PDC core barrels in the Rocky Mountain region. Contact us for a quote or to learn more about our products.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white">Get Your Free Quote</a>
